Class Summary
AMDPresenter The presenter for displaying AnnotatedMapDescriptors in a drop-down list box style interface.
AnnotatedMapPresenter Presenter for annotated map data - handles all mouse events associated with the map including pan/zoom and clicking of elements.
CpdDisambiguationPresenter Presenter used to disambiguate between two compounds with the same synonym.
ExperimentPresenter Presenter for viewing the set of experiments available to an organism.
ExperimentUploadPresenter Presenter for the form that enables users to upload experiment data.
ImagePopupPresenter Presenter for an image that displays a popup when clicked.
InterpolatorPresenter Presenter for summarizing the interpolator used to map measurements onto their target type for a given sample.
LoadingPresenter Presenter for a popup that should be displayed when an operation is taking a "long" time, where "long" is defined by the implementor.
LoginPresenter Presenter for logging a user in and out, as well as displaying login status.
MapElementPresenter Presenter for the map element popups.
MiniMapPresenter Presenter for the mini-map (icon currently displayed in the lower left corner of the screen) for this map.
OrganismPresenter Presenter for viewing the list of organisms available to the user.
OrganismUploadPresenter Presenter for the form that enables users to upload organism data.
PanZoomControlPresenter Presenter for pan/zoom control panel.
ReactionPresenter Presenter for displaying reaction data for a map element.
RetrosynthesisPresenter Presenter for compound, reaction, and gene search, as well as discovery of retrosynthetic pathways via a variety of algorithms.
RxnPopupPresenter Presenter for reaction popups.

OrganismUploadPresenter.FormField Public enum for organism upload form field names.
RetrosynthesisPresenter.Algorithm Enumerated type for available retrosynthesis algorithms.
